Q:Are all mortal wounds inflicted by a Psychic ability, including any caused to the unit with that ability, inflicted by a Psychic Attack?A:Yes.


Q:Do Doombolt (psychic) and similar abilities count as Psychic Attacks for the purposes of the Feel No Pain ability against Psychic Attacks?A:Yes.


Q:When Hazardous weapons inflict one or more mortal wounds as a result of a failed Hazardous test, if that weapon is also a Psychic weapon, are those mortal wounds inflicted by a Psychic Attack?A:Yes.
















